To design and implement a Library automation bot to assist students to identify books kept in various shelfs.
To design a line follower robot to guide students.
To collect data regarding library structure and its methodology of arranging books.
To collect data regarding number of books and its positions.
To combine library data and create a plan to lay down lines for the robot to follow.
To design data transmission and receiving methodology from line follower, so as to communicate data regarding books.
To find or design websites/apps/softwares to send and receive data from the line follower.
